reviewText:
+

Wide range of resolutions (Even for laptops, I was surprised);
Various types of weaponry;
Weather effects (Fog, rain, sun.);
Big open world;
Bunch of side missions and main missions;
Sound options;
Great themed radio stations;
Great voice acting;
Great plot;
Lenghty game.

-

Mute protagonist;
No graphical options;
Weak physics;
No ingame map;
If you fall into the water, you're dead;
Can't get out of the car while it moves. (If the car is on fire and you are driving it full speed you're gonna die.);
No auto-save.

Played it at 1366 x 768 x 32 with 30 Fps cap, max allowed on my laptop.

Score: 8/10.

